{"lemma":"مُخَرَّمَةٍ","slug":"مُخَرَّمَةٍ","root":"خ.ر.م","root_slug":"خ-ر-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-م","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10470","n10471"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10470","headword_ar":"مَخْرِمٌ","root":"xrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end of a prominence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"projecting part, of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaArimu","text_ar":"مَخَارِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxorimu","text_ar":"مَخْرِمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabalK","text_ar":"جَبَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the prominence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"projecting part, of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaromN","text_ar":"خَرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxorimu sayolK","text_ar":"مَخْرِمُ سَيْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremity of a torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K: [accord. to the TK,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a sword;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxrm Alsyf","text_ar":"مخرم السيف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxrm Alsiyl","text_ar":"مخرم السِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) pl. as above: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxorimu A^akamapK","text_ar":"مَخْرِمُ اَكَمَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AkmpK","text_ar":"اكمةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuromu","text_ar":"خُرْمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place where a hill such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Akmp","text_ar":"اكمة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ends."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"road such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two mountains:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaArimu","text_ar":"مَخَارِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mouths of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mountain-roads such as are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fijaAj","text_ar":"فِجَاج"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"roads in rugged tracts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Skr, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"roads in mountains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in sands."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamiynN *aAtu maxaArima","text_ar":"يَمِينٌ ذَاتُ مَخَارِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An oath in which are ways of evasion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA xayora fiY yamiynK laA maxaArima lahaA","text_ar":"لَا خَيْرَ فِى يَمِينٍ لَا مَخَارِمَ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no good in an oath that has not ways of evasion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxorimN","text_ar":"مَخْرِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"between two mountains. ” (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi yamiynN qado TalaEato fiY","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ يَمِينٌ قَدْ طَلَعَتْ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaxaArimi","text_ar":"المَخَارِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is an oath that has come forth in expressions that admit of ways of evasion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: said of an oath that affords a way [or rather ways] of evasion to the utterer thereof. (AZ, TA.) ―         -b2-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaxaArimu","text_ar":"المَخَارِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaArimu All~ayoli","text_ar":"مَخَارِمُ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first portions of the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) It occurs in an instance in which some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaHaArimu","text_ar":"المَحَارِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoramN","text_ar":"مَحْرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","Skr","K"]},{"entry_id":"n10471","headword_ar":"مُخّرَّمٌ","root":"xrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoramu","text_ar":"اَخْرَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahaY A^ano","text_ar":"نَهَى اَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuDaH~aY biAlmuxar~amapi AlA^u*uni","text_ar":"يُضَحَّى بِالمُخَرَّمَةِ الاُذُنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He forbade the sacrificing as an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uDoHiy~ap","text_ar":"اُضْحِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the animal having the ear cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mutilated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having many perforations,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slits, in its ear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}